HEADWORD: Garcinia
<hw>Gar*cin"i*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of plants, including the mangosteen tree
(<spn>Garcinia Mangostana</spn>), found in the islands of the Indian
Archipelago; -- so called in honor of Dr.
<etsep>Garcin</etsep>.</def>⟦br⟧
